41:58.894 --> 42:00.270
LARS: It's okay, Carmel.

42:01.563 --> 42:02.731
Come on.

42:02.731 --> 42:04.399
Let me take you to your room.

42:05.067 --> 42:06.944
Come on. It's okay.

