talk to him, you can.

47:40.903 --> 47:42.321
‐ Via psychedelics?

47:42.321 --> 47:44.031
MASHA: Yes.
‐ Right. Yeah.

47:44.031 --> 47:45.616
I'm sorry. That just sounds like madness.

47:45.616 --> 47:46.700
‐ But it's not madness.

47:46.700 --> 47:48.827
It's dangerous if it's not
managed correctly,

47:48.827 --> 47:51.038
but it is not madness.

47:51.038 --> 47:52.706
‐ This is why we're here.

47:54.166 --> 47:55.876
This is why you chose us.

47:57.377 --> 47:59.171
‐ Because I wanna help you.

48:01.715 --> 48:03.884
