48:12.226 --> 48:13.810
Think of it.

48:13.810 --> 48:15.395
If this works...

48:17.064 --> 48:19.024
imagine what we can offer them.

48:19.566 --> 48:21.652
Because what we can do
is we can offer them

48:21.652 --> 48:23.695
the chance to relieve past trauma.

48:23.695 --> 48:27.074
We can offer them the chance
to come to terms with it,

48:27.533 --> 48:29.576
to share those terms...

48:33.455 --> 48:35.832
with the object of their grief.

48:36.416 --> 48:38.502
Like Zachary for you.

48:39.253 --> 48:42.381
‐ Mm‐mm.
No. I go back to madness.

48:46.426 --> 48:47.761
‐ Heather.

48:47.761 --> 48:49.555
I know pain.

48:49.555 --> 48:50.764
I know it.

48:52.140 --> 48:54.184
And I also know healing.

48:54.893 --> 48:59.606
Put yourself in my hands
and under my care, my control.

49:00.190 --> 49:03.443
I will try to give you your son back.

49:25.716 --> 49:28.594
CARMEL: Well... you found my spot.

49:29.344 --> 49:32.139
