‐ Definitely strange.

49:41.356 --> 49:42.357
CARMEL: Yeah.

49:44.484 --> 49:45.736
How you doing?

49:46.820 --> 49:48.906
‐ Oh, you know.

49:50.365 --> 49:51.700
‐ I actually do.

49:58.582 --> 50:02.169
